    "updated_at": "2025-11-17T17:46:30Z",
    "body": "> The job module already has some options for configuring thresholds.\n\nYes, but they don't have impact on this bug. Even raising the threshold leads to the same behavior. The only way to solve this with an option would be to exclude a specific process name or pattern from the count that is used for the indicator.",
