    "updated_at": "2025-11-17T18:54:24Z",
    "body": "I would say it is unlikely that excluding processes by name well be implemented in the near future. It may be possible for you to change the module format string to `'([$symbol$number]($style) )'`.\nSince other shells usually don't hit this bug, perhaps nushell can optimise the timing auf launching background jobs for cases like this.",
